ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/3547/documentation

This activity provides an average transport in a passenger car of the class EURO 3 with internal combustion engine. The inventory is a linking activity, that links the more specific products in the category EURO 3  to an average product.

This activity provides an average transport, passenger car in the categpry EURO 3.
